title: "Jobs";

import TitleHeader from "../components/TitleHeader.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Jobs">
  <div class="container">
    <TitleHeader>Jobs</TitleHeader>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8">
        <h3>Work with MapLibre</h3>

        <p>
          MapLibre is a community-driven open-source project supported by a
          small core team and a global network of contributors.
        </p>

        <p>We currently do not have any open positions.</p>

        <h3>Contributing to MapLibre</h3>

        <p>
          Our project depends on people who contribute code, documentation,
          ideas, and ecosystem integrations. These contributions are what move
          MapLibre forward.
        </p>

        <p>
          Rather than offering transactional rewards for individual tasks,
          MapLibre focuses on recognizing <strong
            >sustained, high-quality contributions</strong
          > across the project.
        </p>

        <p>
          Contributors who make meaningful impact - whether through features,
          bug fixes, documentation, or community work - are regularly recognized
          by the project. This includes quarterly recognition and, where
          possible, financial rewards tied to overall impact rather than
          individual issues.
        </p>

        <p>
          This approach allows us to support the long-term health of the project
          while fairly acknowledging the people who continuously improve it.
        </p>

        <h3>Get involved</h3>

        <ul>
          <li>Contribute code, bug fixes, or new features</li>
          <li>Improve documentation and examples</li>
          <li>Maintain or build ecosystem integrations</li>
          <li>Help others through issues and discussions</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          Strong contributors often become closely involved in shaping the
          direction of MapLibre over time.
        </p>

        <h3>Future opportunities</h3>

        <p>
          If you're interested in working with MapLibre in the future, feel free
          to reach out at
          <a href="mailto:jobs@maplibre.org">jobs@maplibre.org</a>.
        </p>

        <p>We’ll get in touch if opportunities open up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
